        <h1>
          Get through your email faster
        </h1>
        <p>
          Email is great, except when there’s too much of it. Priority Inbox automatically
          identifies your important email and separates it out from everything else, so you can
          focus on what really matters.
        </p>
        <div id="visual">
          <object class="c1" data=
